-- Russian President May Visit Island Disputed With Japan Today, Kyodo Says
-- B y   F e r g u s   M a g u i r e
-- 2010-10-31T21:46:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-31/russian-president-may-visit-island-disputed-with-japan-today-kyodo-says.html
Russian President Dmitry Medvedev
plans today to visit a Russian-held island that is claimed by
Japan, Kyodo News said, citing unidentified officials.   The trip to Kunashiri will make Medvedev the first Russian
leader to visit one of the disputed islands called the Northern
Territories in Japan and the Southern Kurils in Russia, the
report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Fergus Maguire at 
 fmaguire@bloomberg.net  